post-image" alt="方丹特区" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-Photo-by-Valeria-Magri_SOPA-Images_LightRocket-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-Photo-by-Valeria-Magri_SOPA-Images_LightRocket-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-Photo-by-Valeria-Magri_SOPA-Images_LightRocket-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-Photo-by-Valeria-Magri_SOPA-Images_LightRocket-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-Photo-by-Valeria-Magri_SOPA-Images_LightRocket-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Fontaines-DC-Photo-by-Valeria-Magri_SOPA-Images_LightRocket-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>为了声援巴勒斯坦<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-dc">，方丹</a>取消了计划在伊斯坦布尔举行的演出，他说：“我们必须明确我们的信念。” </p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="251" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/great-escape-2024-boycott-barclays-gaza-palestine-bands-explain-interview-3756631"><b>艺术家们谈论抵制“大逃亡”以声援巴勒斯坦</b></a></li></ul><p>乐队原定于 8 月 20 日在伊斯坦布尔的 Zorlu PSM 场地演出，但在与“巴勒斯坦艺术家和人权活动人士”交谈后，乐队决定取消计划的演出，并为购买门票的粉丝提供全额退款。</p><p>乐队引用了“全球抵制、撤资和制裁 (BDS) 运动”，该运动声称 Zorlu Energy 部分拥有一家供应以色列 5% 至 8% 能源的工厂，之后一直呼吁艺术家拒绝在该场地演出。</p><p> Fontaines DC 在其 Instagram Stories 上的一篇帖子中写道：“由最大的巴勒斯坦联盟领导的全球抵制、撤资和制裁 (BDS) 运动呼吁艺术家拒绝玩 Zorlu PSM，直到 Zorlu 完全放弃对 Zorlu PSM 的供应。以色列正在实施国际法院现在认为可能是种族灭绝的行为。</p><p> “我们真的很期待访问美丽的伊斯坦布尔并玩耍，但在这种情况下，我们必须明确我们的信念，并将与巴勒斯坦人民的声援放在第一位。我们保证一旦有可能就去土耳其比赛。”</p><p>你可以看看下面的帖子： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-H5lobAs6b/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113